text: Ordered yellow rice with chicken for office celebration. Good feedback from colleagues. Good food with good cause. Do support. Admin is friendly and effective as well. Delivery is on time. Value for money
Ordered via Foodpanda and gosh, the portion is huge for the price.. Pls support. Can consider delivery if not convenient to buy directly.. really affordable

Food that I like: croissant or bread (choice of tuna or egg mayo, comes with vegetables such as lettuce, cucumber and tomato), cookies (the one with cranberries in it is very nice and addictive), chicken mushroom pie (I love this when it’s warm and a bit crispy - otherwise I’ll heat up briefly in a toaster)

The cafe is run by persons in recovery, do be patient with the staff and the wait if you intend to support them :)
